               <div class=\"g-panel\">\n                                <div class=\"circle-bg\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"g-menu-contents-wrap\">\n                                    <div class=\"g-menu-contents\">\n                                        <div class=\"g-menu-top flex-container\">\n                                            <h1 class=\"g-menu-logo\">\n                                                <a href=\"../\"><img src=\"../images/common/logo-white.png\" alt=\"第一商事株式会社\"></a>\n                                            </h1>\n                                            <div class=\"g-menu-sns flex-container\">\n                                                <div class=\"sns-instagram\">\n                                                    <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/daiichishoji/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                                                        <img src=\"../images/common/sns-instagram.svg\">\n                                                    </a>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <div class=\"sns-facebook\">\n                                                    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/people/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%95%86%E4%BA%8B%E6%A0%AA%E5%BC%8F%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE/100063544652436/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                                                        <img src=\"../images/common/sns-facebook.svg\">\n                                                    </a>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <div class=\"sns-x\">\n                                                    <a href=\"https://x.com/daiichi3241\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                                                        <img src=\"../images/common/sns-x.svg\">\n                                                    </a>\n                                                </div>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"g-menu-middle\">\n                                            <nav class=\"g-main-menu\">\n                                                <ul>\n                                                    <li class=\"has-child\">\n                                                        <a class=\"g-nav-title\" tabindex=\"-1\">会社案内</a>\n                                                        <ul>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../message/\">社長ご挨拶</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../company/\">企業情報</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../access/\">本社・事業所・関連会社</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../permit/\">許認可</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../company/#company-movie\">会社紹介MOVIE</a></li>\n                                                        </ul>\n                                                    </li>\n                                                    <li class=\"has-child\">\n                                                        <a class=\"g-nav-title\" tabindex=\"-1\">サービス</a>\n                                                        <ul>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../building/\">ビルメンテナンス事業</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../designated/\">指定管理者事業・PFI事業</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../welfare/\">介護福祉事業</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../other/\">その他の事業</a></li>\n                                                        </ul>\n                                                    </li>\n                                                    <li class=\"has-child\">\n                                                        <a class=\"g-nav-title\" tabindex=\"-1\">リクルート</a>\n                                                        <ul>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../work/\">私たちの仕事</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a href=\"../data/\">数字で見る第一商事</a></li>\n                                                            <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.talent-clip.jp/dai-ichi-recruit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">求人サイト</a></li>\n                                                        </ul>\n                                                    </li>\n                                                    <li class=\"no-child\"><a class=\"g-nav-title\" href=\"../news/\">新着情報</a></li>\n                                                    <li class=\"no-child\"><a class=\"g-nav-title\" href=\"../privacy/\">個人情報保護について</a></li>\n                                                    <li class=\"no-child\"><a class=\"g-nav-title\" href=\"../employee-portal/\">社員専用ページ</a></li>\n                                                </ul>\n                                            </nav>    \n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"g-menu-bottom\">\n                                            <div class=\"inner-wrap flex-container\">\n                                                <div class=\"left-box\">\n                                                    <p class=\"tel-title\">お電話でのお問い合わせ</p>\n                                                    <p class=\"tel-number\">019-651-3241</p>\n                                                    <p class=\"tel-time\">受付時間：平日9:00～17:00</p>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <div class=\"right-box\">\n                                                    <div class=\"g-contact-button\">\n                                                        <a href=\"../contact/\">お問い合わせフォーム</a>\n                                                    </div>                                  \n                                                </div>    \n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </header>\n            <main>\n                <div class=\"button-fix-entry\">\n                    <a href=\"https://www.talent-clip.jp/dai-ichi-recruit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"pc-on\" src=\"../images/work/button-entry.png\" alt=\"求人サイトはこちら\"><img class=\"sp-on\" src=\"../images/work/button-entry-sp.png\" alt=\"求人サイトはこちら\"></a> \n                </div>\n                <div class=\"lower-pagetitle-recruit\">\n                    <div class=\"recruit-mv-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"recruit-title-sp sp-on\">\n                            <h1 class=\"pagetitle-h1\">\n                                <span class=\"font-rubik\">Recruit</span>\n                                採用情報\n                            </h1>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"recruit-mv-text-box pc-on\">\n                            <h1 class=\"pagetitle-h1\">\n                                採用情報\n                                <span class=\"font-rubik\">Recruit</span>\n                            </h1>\n                            <p class=\"recruit-mv-copy\">あなたらしく輝く<br>\n                                未来のステージへ</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"recruit-mv-slide\">\n                            <div class=\"swiper swiper-mv\">\n                                <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide01\">\n                                         <img class=\"pc-on\" src=\"../images/work/pc-slide-photo-01.jpg\" alt=\"警備員・清掃員のスタッフ\">\n                                         <img class=\"sp-on\" src=\"../images/work/sp-slide-photo-01.jpg\" alt=\"警備員・清掃員のスタッフ\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide02\">\n                                        <img class=\"pc-on\" src=\"../images/work/pc-slide-photo-02.jpg\" alt=\"指定管理者・施設管理のスタッフ\">\n                                        <img class=\"sp-on\" src=\"../images/work/sp-slide-photo-02.jpg\" alt=\"指定管理者・施設管理のスタッフ\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-slide swiper-slide03\">\n                                        <img class=\"pc-on\" src=\"../images/work/pc-slide-photo-03.jpg\" alt=\"保育・介護のスタッフ\">\n                                        <img class=\"sp-on\" src=\"../images/work/sp-slide-photo-03.jpg\" alt=\"保育・介護のスタッフ\">\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"scroll-box pc-on\"><p class=\"font-rubik\">SCROLL</p></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"recruit-content\">\n                    <div class=\"recruit-content-wrapper\">\n                        <section id=\"recruit-about\">\n                            <div class=\"flex-container\">\n                                <div class=\"image-box\">\n                                    <img src=\"../images/work/photo-about.png\" alt=\"We support your growth!\">\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"title-about font-title\"><span class=\"marker\">安心の環境</span> が<br> <span class=\"marker\">あなたの成長</span> を支える。</h2>\n                                    <p>第一商事では、社員が安心して<br>\n                                       働くことが出来る環境を整えております。<br>\n                                       働く方々が自分らしく活躍できる場を作ることで、<br>\n                                       日々の仕事にも良い影響があると信じています。<br>\n                                       これからも、社員の自己実現を応援して参ります。\n                                    </p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </section>\n                        <section id=\"recruit-works\">\n                            <h2 class=\"title-h2\">Works<span class=\"title-small\">私たちの仕事</span></h2>\n                            <div class=\"works-wrapper flex-container\">\n                                <div class=\"works-box works-building\">\n                                    <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-works-building.jpg\" alt=\"床清掃の様子\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                        <h3 class=\"title-works-kinds\">ビルメンテナンス業</h3>\n                                        <p>幅広い清掃サービスを展開し、建物の「清潔さ」や「快適」を守るお手伝いをしています。</p>\n                                        <div class=\"guide-link\">\n                                            <a href=\"../building/\">詳細を見る</a>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"works-box works-designated\">\n                                    <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-works-designated.jpg\" alt=\"イスをセッティングする様子\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                        <h3 class=\"title-works-kinds\">指定管理事業・PFI事業</h3>\n                                        <p>施設の個性に合わせた運営を行い、地域の皆様に親しまれる施設となるよう取り組んでおります。</p>\n                                        <div class=\"guide-link\">\n                                            <a href=\"../designated/\">詳細を見る</a>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"works-box works-welfare\">\n                                    <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-works-welfare.jpg\" alt=\"介護をする様子\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                        <h3 class=\"title-works-kinds\">介護福祉事業</h3>\n                                        <p>ご利用者様が、自分らしく安心して過ごすことができる様々な介護サービス事業を行っております。</p>\n                                        <div class=\"guide-link\">\n                                            <a href=\"../welfare/\">詳細を見る</a>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </section>\n                        <section id=\"recruit-staff\">\n                            <div class=\"top-wave pc-on\"><img src=\"../images/common/wave-white.png\"></div>\n                            <div class=\"top-wave sp-on\"><img src=\"../images/common/wave-blue-sp-footer.png\"></div>\n                            <h2 class=\"title-h2\">Staff<span class=\"title-small\">第一商事で働く人たち</span></h2>\n                            <div class=\"inner-wrap\">\n                                <div class=\"swiper-staff\">\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">佐藤<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-building\"><span>業務部機動班</span><span>清掃業務</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-sato.jpg\" alt=\"清掃業務　佐藤さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">大沼<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-building\"><span>業務部ガラス清掃</span><span>ガラス清掃</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-onuma.jpg\" alt=\"ガラス清掃　大沼さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">仲山<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-building\"><span>施設管理部</span><span>貯水槽清掃、水質検査</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-nakayama.jpg\" alt=\"貯水槽清掃、水質検査　仲山さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">田村<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-building\"><span>警備部</span><span>警備業務</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-tamura.jpg\" alt=\"警備業務　田村さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">関口<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-designated\"><span>事業部</span><span>指定管理業務</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-sekiguchi.jpg\" alt=\"指定管理業務　関口さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">熊谷<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-welfare\"><span>介護事業部</span><span>介護業務</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-kumagai.jpg\" alt=\"介護業務　熊谷さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                                            <div class=\"staff-info flex-container\">\n                                                <p class=\"staff-name\">千田<span class=\"text-small\">さん</span></p>\n                                                <p class=\"staff-belonging belong-welfare\"><span>介護事業部</span><span>保育業務</span></p>\n                                            </div>\n                                            <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-staff-chida.jpg\" alt=\"保育業務　千田さんの写真\"/></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"swiper-button-box\">\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-button-prev\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-pagination\"></div>\n                                    <div class=\"swiper-button-next\"></div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </section>\n                        <section id=\"recruit-environment\">\n                            <h2 class=\"title-h2\">Environment<span class=\"title-small\">働く環境について</span></h2>\n                            <div class=\"environment-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"environment-box flex-container box-blue\">\n                                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                        <h3 class=\"environment-title-h3\">資格支援</h3>\n                                        <p>業務に関連する資格取得に対し、積極的な支援を行っております。無資格・未経験でも安心して働いていただくために、OJTによる実地研修と研修受講を体系的に行い、スキル向上を目指すことができます。</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"image-box\">\n                                        <img src=\"../images/work/photo-environment-shikaku.jpg\" alt=\"新人に指導をする先輩社員\">\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"environment-box flex-container box-blue\">\n                                    <div class=\"image-box\">\n                                        <img src=\"../images/work/photo-environment-ryoritsu.jpg\" alt=\"老保一体型の保育園で保育をする様子\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                        <h3 class=\"environment-title-h3\">両立支援</h3>\n                                        <p>生活と仕事を両立できるよう、育児・介護を中心とした支援を実施しております。様々なライフステージに合わせた働き方が求められる昨今、会社としても働きやすい環境を整備するための取組を続けております。</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"environment-box box-blue\">\n                                    <h3 class=\"environment-title-h3\">えるぼし、くるみん、いわて女性活躍認定企業</h3>\n                                    <div class=\"flex-container\">\n                                        <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                            <p>厚生労働大臣より、「女性活躍推進企業」および「子育て世代サポート企業」、岩手県より「いわて女性活躍認定企業」の認定を受け、女性や子育て世代が働きやすい企業であることが認められました。事業所内保育施設の運営や育児のための時短勤務等の制度により、長く働き続けられる職場づくりに注力しております。</p>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <div class=\"image-box\">\n                                            <img src=\"../images/work/logo-josei.png\" alt=\"るぼし、くるみん、いわて女性活躍認定企業のロゴ\">\n                                        </div>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"environment-box flex-container box-blue\">\n                                    <div class=\"image-box\">\n                                        <img src=\"../images/work/photo-environment-ohanami.jpg\" alt=\"お花見会の様子\">\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                                        <h3 class=\"environment-title-h3\">お花見会</h3>\n                                        <p>創立記念日である5月1日にちなみ、5月1日の前後に毎年全社員を対象としたお花見会を開いています。日々、別々の現場で働く人たちが、一同に集まる交流の場として当会を実施しております。また、10年～40年まで10年ごとに永年勤続表彰をしており、お互いの仕事を讃えあい、親睦を深めます。</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </section>\n                        <section id=\"recruit-lower-link\">\n                            <div class=\"top-wave pc-on\"><img src=\"../images/common/wave-white.png\"></div>\n                            <div class=\"top-wave sp-on\"><img src=\"../images/common/wave-white-sp-lower.png\"></div>\n                            <div class=\"flex-container\">\n                                <div class=\"link-date-box\">\n                                    <a href=\"../data/\">\n                                        <h2 class=\"title-h2 flex-container\">Data<span class=\"title-small\">数字で見る第一商事</span></h2>\n                                        <div class=\"image-box\"><img src=\"../images/work/photo-data.jpg\" alt=\"数字で見る第一商事のイメージ画像\"></div>\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"link-entry-box\">\n                                    <h2 class=\"title-h2\">Entry<span class=\"title-small\">ご応募はこちらから</span></h2>\n                                    <div class=\"guide-link-blue\">\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.talent-clip.jp/dai-ichi-recruit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">求人サイト</a>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </section>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </main>\n            <footer id=\"footer\">\n                <section class=\"footer-contact\">\n                    <div class=\"flex-container\">\n                        <div class=\"left-box\">\n                            <h2 class=\"title-h2\">Contact<span class=\"title-small\">お問い合わせ</span></h2>\n                            <p>各種サービスご依頼の際は、<br class=\"pc-on\">\n                                お電話またはお問い合わせフォームより<br class=\"pc-on\">\n                                お気軽にご相談ください。\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"right-box\">\n                            <p class=\"title\">お電話でのお問い合わせ</p>\n                            <div class=\"contact-info flex-container\">\n                                <p class=\"tel-number\">019-651-3241</p>\n                                <p class=\"tel-time\">受付時間：平日9:00～17:00</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"button-mail\">\n                                <a href=\"../contact/\">お問い合わせフォーム</a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </section>\n                <section class=\"footer-nav\">\n                    <div class=\"top-wave pc-on\"><img src=\"../images/common/wave-blue.png\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"top-wave sp-on\"><img src=\"../images/common/wave-blue-sp-footer.png\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"footer-nav-top flex-container\">\n                        <div class=\"logo flex-container\">\n                            <a href=\"../\"><img src=\"../images/common/logo-white.png\"></a>\n                            <div class=\"address\">\n                                <p>〒020-0887　岩手県盛岡市上ノ橋町8番8号<br>\n                                    TEL：019-651-3241　　FAX：019-651-3245\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <ul class=\"sns flex-container\">\n                            <li>\n                                <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/daiichishoji/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n                                    <img src=\"../images/common/sns-instagram.svg\">\n                                </a>\n              